{
  "stem": "12150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's two choices for the Germans-- eliminate the whole camp with machine guns, or evacuate the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we didn't know which course they're going to take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So as far as I remember, one day, they told us to pack whatever you have-- which we didn't have much of.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everybody had a plate, a knife, a spoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's all we owned, I figure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that we will be-- and they gave us extra bread, and we were marching for days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from there, we didn't have-- and they explained, and this is amazing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They explained to us we wouldn't march if we had transportation, but transportation like trucks is used by the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They didn't assign enough transportation to us, so we have to march to a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They themselves were not happy to march so many miles, the German guards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, the said it on the way, anybody who cannot keep up with the march will be left behind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They said it in advance, and they said try to keep up the tempo because we have a deadline to meet because they didn't spell it out that the Russians are behind us, but we figured it out.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They just said we have a deadline to meet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We have to be at a cert-- that certain a railroad track or station on a certain day, at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "About three days we marched and unfortunately we lost some of our people because they couldn't keep up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was July or August.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was very, very hot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we didn't have water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We had a little water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Wherever we could stop, we-- they let us go into a lake to get a  little water.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
